###

### Create a new appointment
POST {{base_url}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 1,
  "project_id": 2,
  "date": "2025-11-10",
  "time_from": "10:00:00",
  "time_to": "11:00:00"
}

###

### Get all appointments (requires authentication)
GET {{base_url}}/api/appointments/list
Authorization: {{access_token}}

###

### Get an appointment by ID
GET {{base_url}}/api/appointments/show/1
Authorization: {{access_token}}

###

### Update an appointment
PUT {{base_url}}/api/appointments/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{access_token}}

{
  "date": "2025-11-12",
  "time_from": "14:00:00",
  "time_to": "15:00:00"
}

###

### Delete an appointment
DELETE {{base_url}}/api/appointments/1
Authorization: {{access_token}}
